org.waarp.openr66.protocol.http.restv2.utils

Interface XmlSerializable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XmlSerializable.Aliases, XmlSerializable.Businesses, XmlSerializable.Hosts, XmlSerializable.Roles, XmlSerializable.Rules, XmlSerializable.Transfers

    public interface XmlSerializable
    An interface for POJOs used in XML (de)serialization.

    Classes implementing this interface, as well as their fields' classes *MUST* be annotated with the required JAXB annotations to allow the objects to be marshalled and unmarshalled using JAXB.

    See Also:
    Marshaller, Unmarshaller
